Simple Perl script for interrogating the status of a Netgear WPN824v2 router to
determine incoming/outgoing LAN/WLAN/WAN data rates.

Uses Andreas Bernauer's driveGnuPlotStreams.pl Perl script
(http://www.lysium.de/sw/driveGnuPlotStreams.pl) for plotting real
time data over multiple gnuplot windows.
